        <li class="js-agree-list u-Adjust_Mt-16">2. <a href="https://corp.mobile.rakuten.co.jp/guide/privacy/" class="c-Link_Txt-inline-icon" target="_blank">個人情報の取扱い<span class="c-Icon_New-window-l"></span></a></li>
